      own engine is never unfairly blank for an out-of-set glyph -- an A/B divergence here means a
      REAL defect (missing/short advance, or a broken composite-accent outline), not merely a
      codepoint this ticket's MVP scope never baked.
      Font src is "assets/OpenSans-Regular.ttf" -- relative to the test's WORKING_DIRECTORY
      (CMAKE_CURRENT_BINARY_DIR = build/tests/, the repo-wide embed-test convention; the assets/
      dir is copied there by the fonteng_own_embed_sanity CMake block).
