<rml>
<head>
  <style>
    @font-face { font-family: "Sans"; src: "assets/OpenSans-Regular.ttf"; }

    body {
      background: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-family: "Sans";
      font-size: 48px;
      margin: 8px;
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
    }
    span {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0; margin: 0;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    /* EN: forces each span onto its own line so ink bands never overlap horizontally.
       PT: forรงa cada span na prรณpria linha para as bandas de tinta nunca se sobreporem. */
    br { display: block; }
  </style>
  <title>glintfx L1.20-FONTFLIP A/B compare</title>
</head>
